            . I am a currier, the prisoner worked with me about seven years ago, he behaved as the rest of them do, he would fuddle; I know nothing of him since.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17680907-41-person440">
                  William 
                  Neal 
               <interp inst="t17680907-41-person440" type="surname" value="Neal"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17680907-41-person440" type="given" value="William"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17680907-41-person440" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I have known him some years, he has sold hides for me.</p>
               <p>Q. What are you?</p>
               <p>Neal. I am a citizen and a currier.</p>
               <p>Q. Do you know of his being employed by any body besides you?</p>
               <p>Neal. No, I do not.</p>
               <p>Q. How often has he sold hides for you?</p>
               <p>Neal. He has sold hides for me twice, and no more; I never heard he was guilty of any such thing as this before.</p>
               <p>John Wood I have known him about eight or nine years, he worked for me about six years ago; I never knew no harm of him.</p>
